qas.question: What way is used to announce the election of a new pope in Latin?
What should the new pople have been before becoming a pope?
When was the most recent election of a non-cardinal?
When is the last time a non cardinal was elected as pope?
What way is used in the proclamation of the election of a new nun in Latin?

plausible_answers.text: Annuntio vobis gaudium magnum; habemus Papam: Eminentissimum ac Reverendissimum Dominum, Dominum (first name) Sanctae Romanae Ecclesiae Cardinalem
